OL,5, The chief executive of Scottish beer   
OL,6, giant Brewdog has been accused of      
OL,7, inappropriate behaviour and abuse of   
OL,8, power in the workplace by former staff.
OL,10,FMore than 15 ex-Brewdog workers have   
OL,11,Fspoken out about CEO James Watt to the 
OL,12,FBBC's Disclosure programme.            
OL,14,FFormer Brewdog USA workers said Mr     
OL,15,FWatt's behaviour made female bartenders
OL,16,Ffeel "uncomfortable" and "powerless".  
OL,18,FLawyers for Mr Watt said the           
OL,19,Fallegations were false and he denied   
OL,20,Fbehaving inappropriately.              
